Heating oil for November_DATE delivery ended at 58.64_MONEY cents_MONEY a gallon , up one_MONEY cent_MONEY on the New_ORGANIZATION York_ORGANIZATION Mercantile_ORGANIZATION Exchange_ORGANIZATION . 
